{
  "stem": "747.6",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I didn't think that I would be able to have any children, like none of my friends.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Thank God, I didn't go through Mengele's experiment camp, but just being on a-- such a long time on a starvation diet, it's-- a lot of women couldn't have children afterwards.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So they're good children.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I'm very grateful.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we have seven grandchildren.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They're all darlings, good, and, and following the parents' footstep.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "No problem.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I am very grateful for that.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I think this is the real-- what I got for-- for all the pain, what we went through, this is-- I can't find the word for it to--",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Something like that.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It's not redemption.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Just a-- just a, you know, to consolation--",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Compensation.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yeah, and consolation.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I, I hope they will-- we'll try to instill into them the real sense of values, to be good to other people, respect everyone for what they are, and could be-- world could be so beautiful.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Today, I saw in the paper, in Ecuador, it's starting a war with their neighbors.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Horrible.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I think that I should mention that this friend of mine, who wrote a book, an Italian lady, I can't remember.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Certainly, I can't remember, after 50 years, of her face.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But, certainly, she was with me.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "She wrote a book about her experiences in Auschwitz-Birkenau, and even her number is close to mine.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And she was working in the same commando, the same experience.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I mean, surely, with a different eye because she see-- saw things differently from me.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But the- it came down to it, that, really, when I finish reading her book, I was all excited that I know this woman, not remembering her, but I know she was with me.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "How do I find her?",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
